description: Creates a webhook for a container registry with the specified parameters.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group to which the container registry belongs.

registry_name.description: The name of the container registry.

webhook_create_parameters.description: The parameters for creating a webhook.

properties.description: The properties that the webhook will be created with.

location.description: The location of the webhook. This cannot be changed after the resource is created.
